verbose_text: Thus, taken together, it was of interest to test if deletion of Ido1 could be : (1) compensated by the increased mRNA expression for Ido2 in iLN, (2) impact mRNA expression for downstream genes on kynurenine pathway (Afm, Kmo, Kynu, and Haao) in iLN during CIA, (3) influence the concentration of tryptophan and its anti inflammatory catabolites : kynurenine, AA, and 3-HAA in iLN from Ido1KO mice with CIA, and (4) coincide with reduced concentration of kynurenine in serum of Ido1KO mice with CIA.
evidence: expression for downstream genes on kynurenine pathway (Afm, Kmo, Kynu, and Haao) in iLN during CIA, (3) influence the concentration of tryptophan and its anti inflammatory catabolites: kynurenine, AA, and 3-HAA in iLN from Ido1KO mice with CIA, and (4) coincide with reduced concentration of kynurenine in serum of Ido1KO mice with CIA
